{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"53f638851d","title":"给蔡博等的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1bb02a808b","index":0,"year":1946,"month":1,"day":8,"articleId":"53f638851d","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji4.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"8ac1dd9c88","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"53f638851d","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":1,"offset":17,"text":"蔡博，一九二四年生，湖南湘乡永丰镇（今属双峰县）人，蔡和森之子。张芝明，一九二七年生，江苏常州人，张太雷之子。刘永斌，即刘允斌（一九二五——一九六七），湖南宁乡人，刘少奇之子。黄平，应称尤里黄平，是黄平之子在苏联时用的名字，现名黄健，一九二七年生，广东中山人。赵小炎，即赵施格，一九二八年生，四川酉阳人，赵世炎之子。当时他们均在苏联莫斯科钢铁学院学习。"},{"id":"8dc8a0206b","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"53f638851d","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":2,"text":"永福，即毛岸英（一九二二——一九五○），湖南湘潭人，毛泽东的长子。"}],"contents":[{"id":"35b079ac03","type":"title","text":"给蔡博等的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"53f638851d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ac1dd9c88","type":"paragraph","text":"蔡博、张芝明、刘永斌、黄平、赵小炎诸位青年同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"53f638851d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8dc8a0206b","type":"paragraph","text":"永福回来，接到你们的信，十分高兴。正如你们信上所说，新中国需要很多的学者及技术人员，你们向这方面努力是很适当的。这里，只能简单地写几句话给你们，总之是希望你们一天一天成长，壮健，愉快，进步；并望你们团结一切留苏的中国青年朋友，大家努力学习，将来回国服务。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"53f638851d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc0456e7a5","type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧地握着你们的手！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"53f638851d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dd161d12d4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"53f638851d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1dd064358d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四六年一月八日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"53f638851d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4f2bc39272","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"53f638851d","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45c37b4023","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"53f638851d","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":100,"end":100}}}},"__N_SSG":true}